<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <!-- <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' /> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poiret+One" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Dosis" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div>
                <!-- <i class="fas fa-palette"></i> -->
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">HOME</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">ARCHIVE</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">NEW POST</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">EDIT POST</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">
                        <span>LOG IN</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">
                        <span>SIGN UP</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="heading">
            <div>
                <h1><%= title %></h1>
            </div>
            <p><%= slogan %></p>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="intro">
        <p>Welcome to ANTARTICA, the blog about Art. What is Art? some of you might ask, well, there are many types of art, but to name a few in a nutshell it would be Pencil sketches(Graphite), Grafitti and Painting. Now all of them are different and people enjoy different kinds of art such as looking at what the piece illustrates, because some art can convey deeper meaning then what meets the eye, but lets not dwell on that and get back to enjoying some art.</p>
    </div>
    <main class="featured-blogs">
        <% blogs.posts.forEach(function (item){ %>
        <div class="latest">
            <div class="title">
                <h5><%= item.title %></h5>
            </div>
            <div class="imgBox">
                <img src="<%= item.image %>" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p><%= item.description %></p>
                <p>Author: <%= item.author %></p>
                <p>Date: <%= item.date %></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="contact">
            <h6>ANTARTICA</h6>
            <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i>0844705809</p>
            <p><i class="far fa-envelope"></i>soulcali789@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
        <div class="archive">
            <p><a href="#">Blog Archive</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="other-blogs">
            <h6>OTHER BLOGS</h6>
            <p><a href="http://cooperart.co.za/index.php/artists-blog">Cooperart</a></p>
            <p><a href="http://www.art.co.za/news/">Art</a></p>
            <p><a href="https://www.painters-table.com/blog-roll/artist-blogs">Painters Table</a></p>
            <p><a href="http://painterskeys.com/">Painters Keys</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <div class="designer">
        <p>DESIGNED BY JUSTIN CREIGHTON SCD &copy;2019</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
